title: ATN Owners Meetings Day 2: Les Snead, Dan Quinn & John Harbaugh
itunes:title: ATN Owners Meetings Day 2: Les Snead, Dan Quinn & John Harbaugh
description:
A room filled with heroes- Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Gregg Rosenthal & Chris Wesseling- are live from the Owners Meetings in Orlando, and sit down with Rams GM Les Snead and his wife Kara Henderson, Falcons head coach Dan Quinn and Ravens head coach John Harbaugh.
